e results, we discuss structures, kinematics,\nchemical properties, and the Tully-Fisher relation of S0s in groups.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 May 2011 10:05:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
